text: Florica Silaghi (born 4 May 1957) is a Romanian rower. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Romania Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
